name: Air Canada E-190 Night landing in Calgary
description:
I know I'm not alone in saying this, but...
GOOGLE PLUS SUCKS!
Seriously, they forced me to sign up just so that I could post comments again -_-
But now I have no freaking idea how to reply, so I'm sorry if I don't respond to your comment :( Blame Google.

EDIT: Well, it seems that Google has put the "Reply" button back in its proper spot. I still hate G+ though.

Anyway, here's the last of my inflight videos thus far, my Air Canada E-190 flight landing in Calgary.

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
